#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.88"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.88:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.88:0.2"
msgid "9. Sativagga"
msgstr "9. Mindfulness"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 88. Appasādapavedanīyasutta → appasādappasādasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.88:0.3"
msgid "88. Appasādapavedanīyasutta"
msgstr "88. A Proclamation of No Confidence"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.88:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgatassa bhikkhuno ākaṅkhamānā upāsakā "
"appasādaṃ pavedeyyuṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, the lay followers may, if they wish, make a proclamation of no "
"confidence in a mendicant who has eight qualities."

msgctxt "an8.88:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.88:1.3"
msgid ""
"Gihīnaṃ alābhāya parisakkati, gihīnaṃ anatthāya parisakkati, gihī akkosati "
"paribhāsati, gihī gihīhi bhedeti, buddhassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, dhammassa "
"avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, saṃghassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, agocare ca naṃ passanti."
msgstr ""
"They try to prevent the lay people from getting material possessions. They "
"try to harm lay people. They insult and abuse lay people. They divide lay "
"people against each other. They criticize the Buddha, the teaching, and the "
"Saṅgha. They’re seen at an inappropriate place for collecting alms."

msgctxt "an8.88:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi dhammehi samannāgatassa bhikkhuno ākaṅkhamānā "
"upāsakā appasādaṃ pavedeyyuṃ."
msgstr ""
"The lay followers may, if they wish, make a proclamation of no confidence in "
"a mendicant who has these eight qualities."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.346"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.88:2.1"
msgid ""
"Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgatassa bhikkhuno ākaṅkhamānā upāsakā "
"pasādaṃ pavedeyyuṃ."
msgstr ""
"The lay followers may, if they wish, make a proclamation of confidence in a "
"mendicant who has eight qualities."

msgctxt "an8.88:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.88:2.3"
msgid ""
"Na gihīnaṃ alābhāya parisakkati, na gihīnaṃ anatthāya parisakkati, na gihī "
"akkosati paribhāsati, na gihī gihīhi bhedeti, buddhassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
"dhammassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, saṅghassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, gocare ca naṃ passanti."
msgstr ""
"They don’t try to prevent the lay people from getting material possessions. "
"They don’t try to harm lay people. They don’t insult and abuse lay people. "
"They don’t divide lay people against each other. They don’t criticize the "
"Buddha, the teaching, and the Saṅgha. They’re not seen at an inappropriate "
"place for collecting alms."

msgctxt "an8.88:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi dhammehi samannāgatassa bhikkhuno ākaṅkhamānā "
"upāsakā pasādaṃ pavedeyyun”ti."
msgstr ""
"The lay followers may, if they wish, make a proclamation of confidence in a "
"mendicant who has these eight qualities.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.88:2.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
